{\fs17}and we've never exchanged social calls.

73
00:09:10,582 --> 00:09:13,608
{\fs17}You're right. It's high time I paid a call.

74
00:09:13,685 --> 00:09:17,553
{\fs17}What time? Oh, say, early this afternoon?

75
00:09:17,656 --> 00:09:21,319
{\fs17}I'll be there with a clean shirt and a hungry face.

76
00:09:21,393 --> 00:09:25,659
{\fs17}Do that. You better be going along now.

77
00:09:25,764 --> 00:09:27,664
{\fs17}Don't want to be an accessory after the fact.

78
00:09:29,067 --> 00:09:32,730
{\fs17}You are a considerate man, Capt. Wiles.

