00:15:07,906 --> 00:15:10,704
{\fs17}Wiggy. Wiggy. You haven't sold a painting.

130
00:15:10,809 --> 00:15:12,834
{\fs17}All my pictures in the same place.

131
00:15:12,911 --> 00:15:15,641
{\fs17}So few cars. They don't seem to...

132
