135
00:15:23,822 --> 00:15:25,813
{\fs17}Well, I'm sorry, Mr. Marlow. Let's get a look at your new one.

136
00:15:25,924 --> 00:15:29,724
{\fs17}- Hold it up. - What good would it do to show it to you?

137
00:15:29,761 --> 00:15:32,025
{\fs17}You don't deserve to see it. How am I going to eat?

138
00:15:32,130 --> 00:15:35,463
{\fs17}Mr. Wiggs always used to thump his stomach when he got mad.

139
00:15:35,533 --> 00:15:37,592
{\fs17}He busted somethin' inside once. [Cows Mooing ]

140
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,740
{\fs17}You think we'd do any better on Fifth Avenue?

