159
00:17:04,756 --> 00:17:06,747
{\fs17}Mm-hmm. I only brought up your name once...

160
00:17:06,824 --> 00:17:09,349
{\fs17}when we were talking about strange people.

161
00:17:09,427 --> 00:17:11,918
{\fs17}Huh? That is, strangers...

162
00:17:12,030 --> 00:17:14,521
{\fs17}Oh. People she hadn't met yet.

163
00:17:14,632 --> 00:17:17,157
{\fs17}And, uh, what does the pretty, little thing say about me?

164
00:17:17,235 --> 00:17:21,467
{\fs17}Nothin'. I think we better discuss business.

165
00:17:21,539 --> 00:17:23,939
{\fs17}Here... my shopping list.

166
00:17:24,042 --> 00:17:26,237
{\fs17}I'll go in and start puttin' it up.

167
00:17:36,054 --> 00:17:38,955
{\fs17}Say, Wiggy. How do you spell Tuscaloosa?

168
00:17:39,057 --> 00:17:42,686
{\fs17}Sam?

169
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:44,853
{\fs17}Hi, Calvin. You hear any shootin' a while back?

170
00:17:44,963 --> 00:17:47,693
{\fs17}- Nope. - Well, I did.

171
00:17:47,765 --> 00:17:49,892
{\fs17}And there shouldn't be any shootin' around here. Why?

172
00:17:49,968 --> 00:17:51,902
{\fs17}It's posted land, that's why.

173
00:17:51,970 --> 00:17:55,906
{\fs17}Why's that? 'Cause I posted it.

174
00:17:55,974 --> 00:17:59,171
{\fs17}What you got against people doing a little shooting now and then... let off a little steam?

175
00:17:59,277 --> 00:18:01,871
{\fs17}Bullets and guns are dangerous they injuriously

176
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:05,143
{\fs17}No one around here could hit a freight car with a cannon.

177
00:18:06,617 --> 00:18:09,916
{\fs17}I guess you're right, Sam. All the same, the law's the law.

178
00:18:09,988 --> 00:18:13,151
{\fs17}And I got a good mind to scout around and find out who's doin' the shootin'...

179
00:18:13,224 --> 00:18:15,419
{\fs17}and level a little fine.

180
00:18:15,493 --> 00:18:17,427
{\fs17}And pick up a little piecework?

181
00:18:17,495 --> 00:18:21,989
{\fs17}Well, if I can do anything to make it any harder for you, you let me know.

182
00:19:04,142 --> 00:19:07,543
{\fs17}How'd you want your bacon, Mr. Marlow?

183
00:19:07,578 --> 00:19:11,036
{\fs17}What were you saying? I asked how you want your bacon.

184
00:19:11,149 --> 00:19:14,277
{\fs17}Sliced. [ Doorbells Jingling ]

185
00:19:18,289 --> 00:19:21,452
