186
00:19:23,161 --> 00:19:25,994
{\fs17}[Breathing Deeply] What a wonderful day.

187
00:19:26,064 --> 00:19:28,396
{\fs17}So was yesterday, but you didn't say anything to me about it.

188
00:19:28,466 --> 00:19:31,196
{\fs17}What you want Calvin for?

189
00:19:31,269 --> 00:19:34,170
{\fs17}These marvelous pictures.

190
00:19:34,205 --> 00:19:36,799
{\fs17}Someone told me they were yours.

191
00:19:36,874 --> 00:19:39,968
{\fs17}Why don't you sell them, make a lot of money? Never thought of that.

192
00:19:40,078 --> 00:19:41,978
{\fs17}I guess I'll just have to think about it. And that song...

193
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:45,607
{\fs17}You sing it so beautifully. You wrote it yourself, of course.

194
00:19:45,683 --> 00:19:47,810
{\fs17}What do you want to borrow? Oh, dear.

195
00:19:47,885 --> 00:19:51,048
{\fs17}I just think people need encouragement sometimes. Don't you, Mr. Marlow?

196
00:19:51,122 --> 00:19:54,319
{\fs17}How'd you know my name? Well, it's on the pictures, isn't it?

197
00:19:54,392 --> 00:19:56,326
{\fs17}It's not supposed to be readable.

198
00:19:56,394 --> 00:19:58,624
{\fs17}Oh, you can tell it's not supposed to be. They're very professional.

199
00:19:58,696 --> 00:20:00,891
{\fs17}Don't you think, Mrs. Wiggs?

200
00:20:00,998 --> 00:20:04,957
{\fs17}Well, Miss Gravely, all I know is nobody buys them.

201
00:20:05,036 --> 00:20:08,233
{\fs17}Thank you for yOur encouragement, Miss Gravely.

202
00:20:08,306 --> 00:20:10,297
{\fs17}Well, now I wonder how you know my name?

203
00:20:10,341 --> 00:20:12,707
{\fs17}Easy. Wiggy just said it. Wiggy.

204
00:20:12,810 --> 00:20:15,335
{\fs17}What a perfectly ridiculous little nickname.

205
00:20:15,413 --> 00:20:17,904
{\fs17}Do you mind if I call you Wiggy, Mrs. Wiggs?

206
00:20:18,015 --> 00:20:22,247
{\fs17}Not if you pay all your bills on time. All right, Mr. Marlow.

207
00:20:22,320 --> 00:20:27,917
{\fs17}Bacon, beans, cabbage, sugar, salt, tea, oleo margarine.

208
00:20:28,025 --> 00:20:31,222
